description: While getting supplies at a space station, you meet a robot that speaks a strange language. Transform Dash into a translator to find out what the robot is saying!

puzzles.description: Make Dash randomly choose an FX sound to play.
puzzles.introduction: This strange robot plays a strange sound every time it wants to speak.

hints.description: Link the states with Random Link cues.

puzzles.description: After each FX sound, make Dash play a happy sound when the top button is pressed. Then make Dash return to Start when the top button is pressed again.
puzzles.introduction: Um.  Let's see if Dash understood what the robot said.

hints.description: Link the states with Top Button Pressed cues.

puzzles.description: Replace each happy sound with a custom sound. Record your own message into each custom sound.
puzzles.introduction:
Sounds good to me!  
What do YOU think the robot is saying?

hints.description: Replace each happy sound with a new Custom Sound. Record your own message into each Custom Sound.

puzzles.description: PLAY WITH DASH: Press the top button until you hear each of your recorded sounds.
puzzles.introduction: Now it's time for some deep space communication!
